              quidem illo placeat, maiores magnam velit enim, ea odio, quasi
              rerum?
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-span-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
            <div class="flex w-full items-center gap-2">
              <Image src={PostgreSvg} alt="NextSvg" class="h-12 w-12" />
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl">Databases</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="font-light">
              Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Corporis
              non ipsa dolore repudiandae alias mollitia at nostrum quae quam
              quidem illo placeat, maiores magnam velit enim, ea odio, quasi
              rerum?
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-span-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
            <div class="flex w-full items-center gap-2">
              <Image src={DataSvg} alt="NextSvg" class="h-12 w-12 invert" />
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">DSA</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="font-light">
              Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Corporis
              non ipsa dolore repudiandae alias mollitia at nostrum quae quam
              quidem illo placeat, maiores magnam velit enim, ea odio, quasi
              rerum?
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-span-1 flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
            <div class="flex w-full items-center gap-2">
              <Image src={DockerSvg} alt="NextSvg" class="h-12 w-12" />
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl">Docker</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="font-light">
              Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Corporis
